item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

brad simpson298:

quiet a while and are u sure cause it has torva and lots of new rs items.

That is a 317 server. The client it’s using is loading higher revision data though. For example there are many things that make up the cache: flo, clothing, items, models, anims, gfx, etc… This is a 317 server though. Also, the number is in accordance to the cache. As far as I know no one has created a #617 server to date.

So, to figure out how to do that stuff simply go to the tutorials section and search:

“PI”

There you will find everything you need in order to “maintain” your server.
